body.paragraph:
‘‘Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā asaṅkhataṃ, desito asaṅkhatagāmimaggo. Yaṃ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā. Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyathanijjhāyatha 
Note { id=0, line='3', referenceLine='5', original='nijjhāyatha (ka.)', type='auto', previous='Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā asaṅkhataṃ, desito asaṅkhatagāmimaggo. Yaṃ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā. Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha '
	Alternative{lang='vri', text='Jhāyatha'}
	Alternative{lang='ka.', text='nijjhāyatha'}}
, bhikkhave, mā pamādattha; mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī’’ti. Paṭhamaṃ.

‘‘Acchariyañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi acchariyagāmiñca maggaṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamañca, bhikkhave, acchariyaṃ…pe… abbhutañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi abbhutagāmiñca maggaṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamañca, bhikkhave, abbhutaṃ…pe… anītikañca  vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi anītikagāmiñca maggaṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamañca, bhikkhave, anītikaṃ…pe… anītikadhammañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi anītikadhammagāmiñca maggaṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamañca, bhikkhave, anītikadhammaṃ…pe… nibbānañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi nibbānagāmiñca maggaṃ. Taṃ suṇātha. Katamañca, bhikkhave, nibbānaṃ…pe… abyāpajjhañcaabyāpajjhañca 
